Kenya’s Central Bank Says to Purchase 500 Million Shillings in Repos Today

-- B y   J o h n s t o n e   O l e   T u r a n a
-- 
2011-06-03T09:46:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/kenya-s-central-bank-says-to-purchase-500-million-shillings-in-repos-today.html
Kenya ’s central bank will purchase
500 million shillings through  repurchase agreements  today, a
central bank official said.  The bank won’t make transactions in the foreign exchange
market, the official, who can’t be named in line with the
central bank’s policy, said by phone from Nairobi, the capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Johnstone Ole Turana in Nairobi at 
 jturana@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
